FSQTT.idOfTypicalCourse1: How much has each team member including yourself, contributed to the project?

Course: In the points given below, an equal share is equal to 100 points. e.g. 80 means "Equal share - 20%" and 110 means "Equal share + 10%".
Claimed Contribution (CC) = the contribution claimed by the student.
Perceived Contribution (PC) = the average value of student's contribution as perceived by the team members.
